<style>
  .guest, .appinfo, .login{
    width: 570px;
    border: 2px solid green;
  }
</style>
<h2>Golf Tournament Resgistration App</h2>

<p>All guests can use below features without creating account</p>
  <div class = "guest">
      <ul>
          <li><%= link_to "View the number of registered players", users_path %></li>
          <li><%= link_to "List of Tournaments you can register", tournaments_path %></li>
      </ul>
  </div>

<p>You can find Golf Tournament you wnat to pacticipate here!</p>

<div class="appinfo">
    <ul>

      <p><b>AUTHENTICATION</b></p>

      <li>Users create a new account</li>
      <li>Users login with the created account <b>OR</b> login with GitHub account</li>
      
      <p><b>AUTHORIZATION</b></p>
      
      <li>User can view list of all of the tournaments </li>
      <li>User can view details of individual tournament</li>
      <li>User can register tournament to participate</li>
      <li>User can view all registration from other users</li>
      <li>User can search registration by age</li>
      <li>User can order registration by age</li>

    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>Please sign up or login below to use this application:</p>


  <div class="login">
  <ul>
    <li><%= link_to "Signup as a new user", signup_path %></li>
    <li><%= link_to "Login as an existing user", login_path %></li>
  </ul>
</div>